name: Sea life (refilled)
description: A flocking interactive experiment. This piece evolves when someone buys it. Buy it once and you will be added to the jellyfish list. Buy it twice and you will become a hammerhead shark. Buy it 3 or more times and you will be a killer (crypto-) whale! This is an updated version of OBJKT#18470, that sadly stopped working. Note that it depends on API calls and it might break in the future. Creator: Javier Gracia Carpio | @jagracar
